NAME
       Config::General::Validate

DESCRIPTION

        This module validates a config parsed by Config::General
        against a given hash structure.

INSTALLATION
	to install, type:
	  perl Makefile.PL
	  make
	  make test
	  make install

	to read the complete documentation, type:
	perldoc Config::General::Validate


